</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        +---------------+---------------+
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        |               |               |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    论点A           论点B           论点C
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    （Why）        （What）        （How）
