</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">&gt; </span><span class="ge">核心结论：通过连接池优化+SQL索引+缓存三层策略，
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">&gt; </span><span class="ge">预期接口P99从800ms降至150ms。
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gu">## 一、连接池优化（解决获取连接慢）
